# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:15
translate portuguese adrian2b_fe1843ee:

    # "After work, I check the address that Adrian had sent me and put it into the GPS."
    "Depois do trabalho, verifico a morada que a Adrian me enviou e introduzo-a no GPS."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:16
translate portuguese adrian2b_220b39e6:

    # "It doesn't take long to get to her house. She actually lives really close to my home."
    "Não demora muito a chegar à casa dela. Na verdade, ela mora muito perto da minha casa."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:20
translate portuguese adrian2b_614acdee:

    # "I park on the street, then walk up to the front door and knock. A woman answers almost immediately."
    "Estaciono na rua, depois caminho até à porta da frente e bato. Uma mulher atende quase imediatamente."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:21
translate portuguese adrian2b_3dafc9b9:

    # "Woman" "Hello? Can I help you?"
    "Woman" "Olá? Em que posso ajudar?"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:22
translate portuguese adrian2b_966e8fef:

    # pc "I'm looking for Adrian. Does she live here?"
    pc "Estou à procura da Adrian. Ela mora aqui?"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:23
translate portuguese adrian2b_b542dd0a:

    # "Woman" "Yes she does."
    "Woman" "Sim, mora."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:24
translate portuguese adrian2b_acfd1a5a:

    # pc "She invited me over to play some video games."
    pc "Ela convidou-me para ir lá jogar alguns videojogos."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:25
translate portuguese adrian2b_172cc6dd:

    # "Woman" "Oh she did? She didn't tell me that anybody was coming."
    "Woman" "Ah, é mesmo? Ela não me disse que alguém ia aparecer."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:26
translate portuguese adrian2b_2fdb51d6:

    # "Woman" "You just stay there and I'll go get her."
    "Woman" "Fica aí e eu vou buscá-la."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:27
translate portuguese adrian2b_cddf2662:

    # "Then, I hear footsteps coming down the stairs and Adrian calls out."
    "Então, ouço passos a descer as escadas e a Adrian chama por mim."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:28
translate portuguese adrian2b_9899eaa9:

    # gg "He's my friend, Mom, let him in."
    gg "É meu amigo, mãe, deixa-o entrar."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:33
translate portuguese adrian2b_c583a608:

    # "Woman" "You're supposed to tell me if somebody is coming over, Adrian."
    "Woman" "Devias ter-me dito se alguém vinha cá, Adrian."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:34
translate portuguese adrian2b_6c01d4fd:

    # gg "I know, Mom. I meant to, but I was just busy... with schoolwork. I forgot."
    gg "Eu sei, mãe. Tinha intenção de o fazer, mas estava ocupada... com os trabalhos da escola. Esqueci-me."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:35
translate portuguese adrian2b_e878210c:

    # "Adrian's Mom" "Okay, well he can stay until 10."
    "Adrian's Mom" "Está bem, ele pode ficar até às 22h."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:36
translate portuguese adrian2b_326f12bf:

    # gg "Okay, Mom. Thank you."
    gg "Está bem, mãe. Obrigado."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:39
translate portuguese adrian2b_8f7ebec7:

    # "I follow her inside the house and we walk up the stairs."
    "Sigo-a para dentro de casa e subimos as escadas."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:44
translate portuguese adrian2b_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/adrian_sorry.mp3'
    voice 'voices/adrian_sorry.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:45
translate portuguese adrian2b_c03425eb:

    # gg "I'm sorry about that. She can be a bit overbearing sometimes."
    gg "Desculpa por aquilo. Ela pode ser um pouco autoritária às vezes."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:46
translate portuguese adrian2b_3ed1d973:

    # gg "She's just very protective of me. Only child and all."
    gg "Ela é apenas muito protetora comigo. Filha única e tudo mais."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:49
translate portuguese adrian2b_04c7f126:

    # pc "My dad could be the same way sometimes when I was growing up. I'm an only child too."
    pc "O meu pai podia ser assim às vezes quando eu era criança. Também sou filha única."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:50
translate portuguese adrian2b_f7e6c62b:

    # gg "Then you understand."
    gg "Então compreendes."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:52
translate portuguese adrian2b_636661b2:

    # gg "It does sometimes."
    gg "Às vezes é mesmo assim."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:53
translate portuguese adrian2b_2900eca8:

    # gg "But I love her and she's been really good to me through a lot of hard times."
    gg "Mas adoro-a e ela tem sido muito boa para mim em muitos momentos difíceis."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:54
translate portuguese adrian2b_c07d0332:

    # pc "That's good. Always good to have people there for you."
    pc "Isso é bom. É sempre bom ter pessoas que estão lá para ti."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:55
translate portuguese adrian2b_a560b57e:

    # gg "Want to check out the game?"
    gg "Queres ver o jogo?"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:56
translate portuguese adrian2b_39757b54:

    # pc "Yeah, let's do it."
    pc "Sim, vamos lá."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:59
translate portuguese adrian2b_5c242d3c:

    # gg "Okay, so this is my character. Her name is Trenoxa and she's a mage."
    gg "Ok, então esta é a minha personagem. O nome dela é Trenoxa e ela é uma maga."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:60
translate portuguese adrian2b_290fa501:

    # pc "She looks badass."
    pc "Ela parece durona."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:61
translate portuguese adrian2b_eecdf621:

    # gg "Oh she definitely is. Watch me kill all these kobolds."
    gg "Oh, ela é mesmo. Vê-me a matar todos estes kobolds."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:66
translate portuguese adrian2b_8a0ec2b0:

    # "Using the keyboard and mouse, she guides her character into the middle of a group of small monsters and proceeds to blow them all up."
    "Usando o teclado e o rato, ela conduz a personagem para o meio de um grupo de pequenos monstros e começa a explodi-los a todos."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:68
translate portuguese adrian2b_c9d9899a:

    # "I barely look at the screen, unable to take my eyes off of her."
    "Mal olho para o ecrã, incapaz de tirar os olhos dela."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:69
translate portuguese adrian2b_c68ec5f4:

    # "She really gets into this stuff, and it's cute to see her so excited about it."
    "Ela mete-se mesmo nisto, e é giro vê-la tão entusiasmada com isto."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:72
translate portuguese adrian2b_f57aeacc:

    # gg "Do you want to give it a try?"
    gg "Queres experimentar?"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:73
translate portuguese adrian2b_e3e97310:

    # pc "What if I get your character killed?"
    pc "E se eu matar a tua personagem?"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:74
translate portuguese adrian2b_03db2857:

    # gg "It's no big deal. You just revive at the nearest respawn point and are weakened for a few minutes."
    gg "Não é nada de mais. Basta ressuscitar no ponto de respawn mais próximo e ficas enfraquecido por alguns minutos."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:75
translate portuguese adrian2b_9a5eb084:

    # gg "Come on, give it a try, see if you like it."
    gg "Vá lá, experimenta, vê se gostas."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:76
translate portuguese adrian2b_63023601:

    # pc "Okay."
    pc "Está bem."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:79
translate portuguese adrian2b_2d53ff69:

    # "We switch seats and I play for a bit, trying to learn all the buttons."
    "Trocamos de lugar e eu jogo um pouco, tentando aprender todos os botões."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:80
translate portuguese adrian2b_b0a6ba6f:

    # gg "Okay, all of your powers are the number keys up top. You move with WASD and look around with the mouse."
    gg "Pronto, todos os teus poderes estão nas teclas numéricas lá em cima. Moves-te com WASD e olhas à tua volta com o rato."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:81
translate portuguese adrian2b_3b25da4f:

    # gg "Just click on what you want to kill and then use one of your powers to kill it."
    gg "Basta clicar no que queres matar e depois usar um dos teus poderes para o matar."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:82
translate portuguese adrian2b_b4a8a49d:

    # gg "Super easy. Barely an inconvenience."
    gg "Super fácil. Quase não dá trabalho."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:83
translate portuguese adrian2b_babb66b4:

    # pc "You say that, but I'm still wondering what a WASD is."
    pc "Dizes isso, mas ainda estou a pensar o que é o WASD."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:86
translate portuguese adrian2b_055f2992:

    # "A little bit later, I have pretty much figured out the controls and am demolishing enemies."
    "Um pouco mais tarde, já percebi praticamente os controlos e estou a destruir inimigos."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:87
translate portuguese adrian2b_4915d075:

    # gg "You like it?"
    gg "Gostas?"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:88
translate portuguese adrian2b_3b7f3448:

    # pc "I have to admit, it's pretty fun."
    pc "Tenho de admitir, é bastante divertido."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:89
translate portuguese adrian2b_a82592f5:

    # gg "I'm glad. If you bought a copy sometime, we could even play together."
    gg "Ainda bem. Se comprares uma cópia um dia destes, até podemos jogar juntos."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:90
translate portuguese adrian2b_c0437e5d:

    # pc "That would be fun."
    pc "Isso seria divertido."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:93
translate portuguese adrian2b_ee920117:

    # gg "I think so too. I'd love to explore and kill goblins with you."
    gg "Também acho. Adoraria explorar e matar goblins contigo."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:94
translate portuguese adrian2b_efa756f8:

    # pc "Maybe I'll get it sometime then."
    pc "Talvez compre um dia destes, então."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:95
translate portuguese adrian2b_ce14f6da:

    # gg "Good."
    gg "Ótimo."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:96
translate portuguese adrian2b_6a346fe1:

    # gg "It's about time for you to go. I wouldn't mind hanging out longer, but it's nearly 10 and my mom will be mad."
    gg "Está na hora de ires. Não me importava de ficar mais tempo, mas já são quase 22 horas e a minha mãe vai ficar zangada."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:97
translate portuguese adrian2b_8f70c6ec:

    # pc "Okay, I'll go then. Don't want to get you in trouble."
    pc "Está bem, então vou-me embora. Não quero meter-te em sarilhos."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:98
translate portuguese adrian2b_45175d50:

    # gg "I had a good time though. Thank you for coming over."
    gg "Mas diverti-me imenso. Obrigada por teres vindo."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:99
translate portuguese adrian2b_1b5489ad:

    # pc "Thanks for inviting me, I had fun too."
    pc "Obrigado pelo convite, também me diverti."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:103
translate portuguese adrian2b_6a658ffa:

    # "She walks me down to the front door."
    "Ela acompanha-me até à porta da frente."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:104
translate portuguese adrian2b_2c7e0e7e:

    # gg "I could probably get you a copy of the game. If I did, would you play with me?"
    gg "Provavelmente consigo arranjar-te uma cópia do jogo. Se o fizesse, jogavas comigo?"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:105
translate portuguese adrian2b_7f0c6c37:

    # pc "Yeah, I think I could do that."
    pc "Sim, acho que sim."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:107
translate portuguese adrian2b_d41d8cd9_1:

    # voice 'voices/adrian_seeyou.mp3'
    voice 'voices/adrian_seeyou.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:108
translate portuguese adrian2b_c8b2cdfc:

    # gg "Okay cool. I'll see you in class, [pcname]."
    gg "Ok, fixe. Vemo-nos na aula, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/Adrian2b.rpy:109
translate portuguese adrian2b_9bfc226b:

    # pc "Alright. Bye, Adrian."
    pc "Está bem. Adeus, Adrian."

